%p= @invitation.email + ','
%p
 = @group.user.name + " has invited you to join the fantasy football league " + @group.name
%p
 A message from 
 = @group.user.name 
%p.invitation_message
 = '"' + @invitation.message  + '"'
%p
 To claim your spot and set up your team, follow the link below. Be sure to register using this email address (
 = @invitation.email + ').'
 If you prefer to use a different email account, you can always change it after signing up
